### User Management Tests
###
### Note: This file uses {{accessToken}} variable which should be set from the auth.http file
### Run the login request in auth.http first to get a valid access token
###

### Get User Profile
GET http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/users/0eb81006-a945-4433-ae59-efa779ebfd34/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Update User Profile
PUT http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "updated_username",
  "email": "updated_email@example.com",
  "full_name": "Updated Full Name",
  "bio": "This is an updated bio with more details about the user."
}

###

### Request Account Deletion
POST http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/users/account/delete-request
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Confirm Account Deletion
DELETE http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/users/account
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confirmation_token": "your_confirmation_token_here"
}

###

### Search Users - Default Pagination
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/user-management/users/search

###

### Search Users - Custom Pagination
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/user-management/users/search?limit=10&offset=5

###

### Search Users - Count Only
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/user-management/users/search?count_only=true

###

### Search Users - With Query Parameters
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/user-management/users/search?q=test&limit=5&offset=0

